      <Header />
      <div className="min-h-[calc(100vh-64px)] flex items-center justify-center p-6">
        <div className="bg-white text-black p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-4xl w-full">
          <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-4">üìã ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£</h2>

          {/* Section 1: Personality */}
          <h3 className="mt-6 mb-2 font-semibold">1. ‡∏ö‡∏∏‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û (‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏° 50 ‡∏Ñ‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ô)</h3>
          {[
            "‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤", "‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏™‡∏∞‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏¢", "‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û", "‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏Ç‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏ô", "‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ï‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏£‡πâ‡∏ô",
